[\fB\-\-permanent\fR] [\fB\-\-zone\fR=\fIzone\fR] [\fB\-\-permanent\fR] [\fB\-\-policy\fR=\fIpolicy\fR] \fB\-\-remove\-rich\-rule\fR=\*(Aq\fIrule\fR\*(Aq
