Set new description to ipset
.RE
.PP
\fB\-\-permanent\fR \fB\-\-ipset\fR=\fIipset\fR \fB\-\-get\-description\fR
.RS 4
Print description for ipset
.RE
.PP
\fB\-\-permanent\fR \fB\-\-ipset\fR=\fIipset\fR \fB\-\-set\-short\fR=\fIdescription\fR
.RS 4
Set short description to ipset
.RE
.PP
\fB\-\-permanent\fR \fB\-\-ipset\fR=\fIipset\fR \fB\-\-get\-short\fR
.RS 4
Print short description for ipset
.RE
.PP
[\fB\-\-permanent\fR] \fB\-\-ipset\fR=\fIipset\fR \fB\-\-add\-entry\fR=\fIentry\fR
.RS 4
Add a new entry to the ipset\&.
